Selective Prep Program (for Selective School Entry)

This program prepares students for selective school entrance exams with targeted teaching and practice aligned to ACER and Edutest formats.

Key Features

  • Curriculum aligned with ACER and Edutest formats
  • Small class sizes for personalized attention
  • Custom learning plans and performance feedback
  • Training in exam techniques, time management, and stress reduction
  • Weekend and after-school class options
  • Parental involvement with regular updates

Subjects Covered

  • Mathematics
  • English Language
  • Verbal & Non-Verbal Reasoning
  • Full practice exams with performance analytics

Enrollment Steps

  1. Consultation
  2. Assessment
  3. Registration
  4. Kick-off Session
); }
